The worst part was that I knew I\xe2\x80\x99m deteriorating and doing this to myself. Because I realised it, I had couple attempts at self-de@th, you feel so hopeless, everyday was terrific, I was dying.\n\nBut what saved me was ignorance. Stopped checking nutritional value stickers.
